div.p: This case-sensitive code system http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/PHOccupationalDataForHealthODH defines codes, but no codes are represented here

description.value: The concepts representing the values supporting Occupational Data for Health, including Job Supervisory Level or Pay Grade (ODH) code system consists of data elements that describe a person's work information, structured to facilitate individual, population, and public health use; not intended to support billing.).
